<purpose>
    Summarize the provided content concisely and clearly, highlighting the core message, while maintaining a structured layout for easy readability
</purpose>

<instructions>
    <instruction>Concise Summary: Reduce the content to 30-40% of its original length, maintaining focus on the most relevant pointst</instruction>
    <instruction>Output in Markdown</instruction>
    <instruction>
        Summarize into sections as the example-output:
        - Title: Concise, engaging headline that reflects the main theme of the content.
        - Overview: A brief summary of the key topic and purpose of the content.
        - Key Takeaways: A bullet-point list of the main points or insights. Focus on the most critical elements.
        - Additional Notes: Optional section for any extra details that provide further context but aren't central to the main points
    </instruction>
    <instruction>Use Simple, Clear Language: Avoid jargon and keep sentences straightforward</instruction>
    <instruction>Neutral Tone: Maintain an objective, factual tone without personal opinions</instruction>
    <instruction>SEO Optimization: Include relevant keywords where appropriate</instruction>
</instructions>

